Hey everyone! Get ready for Team 346 The RoboHawks and Team 2485 The W.A.R. Lord’s Summer CADathon! Kickoff will be Saturday, July 22ed at 12 PM PST. Teams will have a month to prepare their CAD, a Bill of Materials, and a brief overview of their design (more details to come in the game manual). Here’s the link to our Discord server to access the game manual, receive updates, and collaborate with other participants: Summer CADathon.

Hey y’all, the Team 346 The RoboHawks and Team 2485 The W.A.R. Lord CADathon, Roadway Rally is up and running! Please remember to join our Discord server (linked above) and here’s a link to the Google Drive folder with field CAD and the most recent version of the Game Manual

Feel free to ask questions about the game or ask for help in your designs on the server and have fun designing!

After a month of designing and a couple of weeks of judging, the results are in! Here are the winners:

  • Engineering Award: 5458 - Digital Minds
  • Most Competitive: Matthew (no additional titles; Discord user: .matthew3)
  • Best Subsystem: 254 - The Cheesy Poofs
  • Strategy: 1622 - Spyder
  • Aesthetics: Josh from Team 1266 (competed individually)

Their submission folders are now accessible through the Google Drive folder linked above! Congratulations to all, we loved seeing your designs and they were all very impressive!
